Name: Description
Preterm Births by Race/Ethnicity: The percentage of babies born alive before 37 weeks of pregnancy. Percents refer to the percentage of all live births.

Name: Source Notes
Preterm Births by Race/Ethnicity: New York City Department of Health and Mental Hygiene, Bureau of Vital Statistics, Summary of Vital Statistics (2000-2019); retrieved from https://www1.nyc.gov/site/doh/data/data-publications/periodic-publications.page.
